snippet: Others were trapped in rubble when a portion of a concrete building fell apart at a military training center in Omsk, near the border with Kazakhstan.
abstract: At least two people are killed at military training center in south-central Russia when a concrete military barracks partly collapses; cause of collapse is unclear.
lead_paragraph: Others were trapped in rubble when a portion of a concrete building fell apart at a military training center in Omsk, near the border with Kazakhstan.

headline.main: At Least 2 Are Killed in Collapse at Russian Barracks
headline.print_headline: Collapse at Russian Barracks Kills at Least Two
